# ENTITY::IS_ENTITY_OCCLUDED

## Summary
Checks if an entity wouldn't be rendered with the current camera, i.e. it is outside the view frustum or it is behind an occluder

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **BOOL**
